OL,3,CThousands gather in Oxford for annual
OL,4,CMay Morning celebrations
OL,6,FThousands of people have welcomed the
OL,7,Fcoming of Spring with the celebration
OL,8,Fof May Morning in Oxford.
OL,10,FAround 18,500 people attended the
OL,11,Flatest edition of the 500-year-old
OL,12,Fevent, which got underway at 6am on
OL,13,FFriday morning.
OL,15,FOxford City Council, which organises
OL,16,Fthe celebrations, said this year it
OL,17,Fwas attended by around 2,000 more
OL,18,Fpeople than in 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
