OL,3,CThousands gather in Oxford for annual
OL,4,CMay Morning celebrations
OL,6,FCrowds lined Magdalen Bridge and
OL,7,FOxford's High Street around Magdalen
OL,8,FTower to hear the Magdalen College
OL,9,FChoir sing a rendition of the latin
OL,10,Fcomposition Hymnus Eucharisticus.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FMorning May brings together the city's
OL,18,Fcommunities, visitors and people of
OL,19,Fall ages to enjoy dancing, singing and
OL,20,Frevelry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
